Author: passcombo.com üè¥‚ò†üçã#0622
Content: @Regnar  if I'm not mistaken opid is Agama internal operation id created before even tx is sent. opid not visible on the block explorer, but visible in the wallet. After tx is created there is just tx id which is visible on block explorer and can be seen publickly.

Author: passcombo.com üè¥‚ò†üçã#0622
Content: for z tx it takes time to create valid z tx, so before you got tx id there is opid. For other wallets the time diff is small enough not to bother with opid probably.
